arStrings.szText: "Did you learn anything from the entrails?"
Yes. Our people are starving, going hungry while the goatmen overrun our farms. These lands used to be protected, but... well, we've no time now for this chatter.
From my readings, I was able to see their attack on Kealer farm, nearby. I sensed a survivor. Hurry! Find them.
Learn what you can, then return to me. I hope it's not too late.
